    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>April 16th 1849</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Revd I. Leeser</addressee>,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">We send you two samples<lb/> of Brocatel. Of the crimson pattern
                    <del>the same as we sent<lb/> you</del>, we have 5 ¼ yds left double width at $5
                that is<lb/> the same as 10 ½ yds of the single width. Of the<lb/> crimson &amp;
                maroon sample we enclose we can send<lb/> you any quantity you wish. It is single
                width,<lb/> price <hi rend="underline">2.50</hi> per yd:</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">We shall be pleased to hear<lb/> from you soon,</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">We are Dr Sir, Your obt servts</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">Solomon &amp; Hart</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(6)"><placeName>243 Broadway</placeName>.</p>
        </body>
